data.description: AGENTS, PLEASE READ REALTOR ONLY REMARKS. This 2 bedroom 2 bath home is located in the Garden Grove Section of Winter Haven. The home has 1,160 sq.ft of living with split bedrooms, ceramic tile and wood laminate floors, large open kitchen and dining area with stainless steel appliances. The home also features a fenced in yard, one car garage, and enclosed rear patio. Community features include pool, private boat ramp, and fishing deck. Hurry, this one won't last long! AGENTS, PLEASE READ REALTOR ONLY REMARKS.
